{"tid":945400,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"又可以準備偷技術～挖孔折疊都落後，三星開始研發全息影像手機","createTime":"2018-12-18T00:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T11:57:35.000Z","uid":141060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63cb4e3d28ae67eff0909fb9673c8a7b1fdb828b","tid":945400,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T00:52:09.000Z","msg":"12月18日消息 如果沒有意外的話，三星將會在明年2月底3月初的MWC大會上發布三星S10系列機型，根據目前的爆料消息來看，該系列機型將會有&ldquo;挖孔屏&rdquo;設計的型號。另外，根據外媒之前的消息，三星可折疊屏幕手機也將在大會上給出更多的消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/12/20181218_071002_553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F12%2F20181218_071002_553.jpg&h=6c7f7a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據外媒給到的更多消息，挖孔屏、折疊屏在三星看來似乎已經不夠用了，這家公司已經開始著手研發全息手機。<br />\n<br />\n在三星最新提交的專利申請當中，我們發現了一項名為&ldquo;全息圖再現設備及其方法&rdquo;的發明專利。通過專利描述，這項技術可能將會用在手機上，讓手機展現全息圖像。<br />\n<br />\n不過，即便目前能夠實現全息手機的生產，那麼這樣的手機的生產成本也是相當的高。根據三星介紹，三星全息手機將會使用一種被三星命名為SLM的元器件，應該是一種空間光調制器，包括光敏層，被配置為根據寫入光束寫入全息圖案；液晶顯示器（LCD）面板設置在光敏層的前表面上，以將入射的再現光束調制成對應於全息圖案的多個衍射光束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/12/20181218_071023_505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F12%2F20181218_071023_505.jpg&h=1b7ecf7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三星尋求的解決方案繞過了目前唯一可用的SLM解決方案的限制（作為消費者目標組件）。這些當前解決方案顯示全息圖像，其分辨率取決於&ldquo;像素間距&rdquo;。像素間距是顯示器上像素的密度。三星的新解決方案是&ldquo;光學尋址的SLM，不受像素間距的影響，並通過光線記錄和再現計算機生成的全息圖案。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/12/20181218_071038_886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F12%2F20181218_071038_886.jpg&h=77d39cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2018/12/20181218_071043_744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2018%2F12%2F20181218_071043_744.jpg&h=2e28910f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在此之前，三星在2017年曾獲得了全息眼鏡相關專利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  立體av"},{"pid":"a8d61a86f19fe8dab37c486c5e0f7a3206703f70","tid":945400,"uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file.elecfans.com/web1/M00/45/51/pIYBAFpoNiuAfSPWAABUCT2B0-s633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile.elecfans.com%2Fweb1%2FM00%2F45%2F51%2FpIYBAFpoNiuAfSPWAABUCT2B0-s633.jpg&h=b249cd09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wiikk.com/upload/default/20180814/d84b49d7fc01c9465ec267ea4194a972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiikk.com%2Fupload%2Fdefault%2F20180814%2Fd84b49d7fc01c9465ec267ea4194a972.jpg&h=ac394b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR4C8KHhc_t6hFV3jJ1WbL6naP-gzjOqEy0kVXKbEe3Km4BD2wNAQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR4C8KHhc_t6hFV3jJ1WbL6naP-gzjOqEy0kVXKbEe3Km4BD2wNAQ&h=95feaeba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2faa1a002e43069f8aaf61655e6e2c65f66bfa09","tid":945400,"uid":14600,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T01:36:31.000Z","msg":"如果係真呢鋪三星真係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d397817ef0ae18aae1a78165d7d822391019b","tid":945400,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"但個影像可唔可以同用家個手勢有互動？冇嘅話，我暫時想像唔到有乜實際用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nanyway, 啲廠鬥出新功能都係好事"},{"pid":"e2cdd61d2e29f1c6523eb136c6f9cb679f042b8f","tid":945400,"uid":51933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:06:48.000Z","msg":"你做到